Invocation Name: miz quotes
des:
Simply tell Alexa to "ask THE MIZ for a quote" to get some ancient wisdom laid upon you... except everything is more about the Miz than it is about you or anybody else in the world.

This skill is only available in English. Some quotes are truly win, some fall flat on their face. All are Miztastic.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
